een sentences, often using transition words. Unity: Each sentence should directly relate to the main topic and contribute to the paragraph\'s overall meaning. Development: Provide sufficient details and examples to support your claims. Types of Paragraphs: Expository: Explains a topic or process. Descriptive: Creates a vivid picture of a</string>
